    /**
     * @description Stores issued master certificates. No write permissions are defined.
     * @path /masterCertificates/{masterCertificateId}
     * @allow (get) Any user can read certificate data.
     * @allow (list) Any user can list certificates.
     * @deny (create) No one can create certificates without specific authorization.
