    /**
     * @description Stores schedule events. No specific write access is defined.
     * @path /schedules/{scheduleId}
     * @allow (get) Any user can read schedule data.
     * @allow (list) Any user can list schedules.
     * @deny (create) No one can create schedules without specific authorization.
